EaglerCraft 26.1.2 - Favicon Placeholder
==========================================

This file is a placeholder note. In a production build, replace this with
an actual favicon.png file (32x32 or 64x64 pixels recommended).

The favicon should be a Minecraft-style icon representing EaglerCraft.
Common approaches:
  - An eagle silhouette over a Minecraft block
  - A pixelated "E" in EaglerCraft brand colors (#e94560)
  - A simplified Minecraft grass block icon

Requirements:
  - Format: PNG (preferred) or ICO
  - Recommended sizes: 16x16, 32x32, 64x64, 128x128
  - Transparency: Use alpha channel for clean edges
  - Color space: sRGB

To generate a proper favicon from an image:
  1. Create a 64x64 or larger source image
  2. Use an online favicon generator or ImageMagick:
     convert source.png -resize 32x32 favicon.png
     convert source.png -resize 16x16 favicon-16.png
     convert source.png -resize 32x32 favicon-32.png
     convert source.png -resize 64x64 favicon-64.png

The index.html references this file via:
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">

Note: The offline download template may embed the favicon as a data URI
to ensure it works without external file access.
